=================
Changing Painting
=================

Overview
--------
Welcome to *Changing Painting*, a generic deployment tool for XML-based artifacts

Requirements
------------

* Python 2.7.6
* Works on Mac OSX

Authors
-------
Changing Painting was created by [William Coronado](https://github.com/wcorona).
